{"tid":5251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現性分析覺得（LIHKG）唔可以代替高登既人","createTime":"2016-11-26T20:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T16:52:27.000Z","uid":14908,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a87aec92b8f27c7bdd1b1909fb7690759c0158a","tid":5251,"uid":14908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:05:28.000Z","msg":"個班人可能好多上左高登十年左右<br />\n對高登有著深厚既感情<br />\n佢地依架就好似d濕鳩藍絲一樣<br />\n覺得自己既現狀好好<br />\n唔需要去改變<br />\n比人踩到上心口都無動於衷<br />\n當有人去做個新壇反一個大壇時候<br />\n佢地就屌鳩人唔撚諗感情<br />\n但大家都知道新壇個app又順又盛<br />\n但有班死硬派依然死守高登<br />\n話有感情，li會唔同感覺<br />\n但呢班人係有人都會屌柒林早洩<br />\n利申，我個人覺得lihkg絕對可以完全取代高登"},{"pid":"e49b8786028646a9fafefa234d6a3a0954cd9cfc","tid":5251,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2ad5ab1ba155c739df635b20f9424c946bae8c","tid":5251,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:28:43.000Z","msg":"有網頁版同an版就可以"},{"pid":"0c1ba3d6bb5c5e24a573f8d179ad96a9b95817c4","tid":5251,"uid":17366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T22:50:08.000Z","msg":"哩度仲似高登過個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7cb591e47ed7c19b41ab37b47efd0c7431b4f6","tid":5251,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T23:06:31.000Z","msg":"用左幾個鐘 已經有返上高登既感覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbdf9ae563424b8774f354b2c22eb8d44d34430","tid":5251,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T23:07:33.000Z","msg":"根本就反映緊香港"},{"pid":"500cf8cadb22406a1e2794aac1fdaf340e3daa83","tid":5251,"uid":14908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就反映緊香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以一定要主力支持 lihkg"}]}